    "claim": "`exchangeRateStoredInternal()` prices cTokens from the raw live underlying balance `balanceOf(address(this))`. Any unsolicited balance increase that does not mint matching cTokens—such as a positive rebase, issuer mint to the market, or other exogenous balance increase—immediately raises the exchange rate used in account snapshots and collateral checks.",
